hcc_text: Bainbridge Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At Bainbridge Avenue at East Fordham Road, East Kingsbridge Road and Elm Place, there were 3 deaths and severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
